{"tid":1503401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以話我知，我地會得到最終勝利","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:41:21.000Z","uid":300229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c66d40cfd0a707c267cea572acd0669ccd9e0d45","tid":1503401,"uid":300229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"我知香港唔會變番以前咁<br />\n但睇住依家既香港<br />\n覺得真係好心寒<br />\n大型機構跪低<br />\n啲狗加強裝備繼續被迫害<br />\n琴晚仲有屋苑因為著黑衫，保安唔認得而令市民無得番屋企<br />\n721未有人入罪<br />\n五大訴求一直被無視<br />\n數以百計手足被控罪<br />\n已經兩個月啦<br />\n知道今次係長期戰<br />\n但有時見到咁既情況<br />\n真好心灰<br />\n搵人話我知丫<br />\n我地係咪會贏?<br />\n係咪大家都會繼續堅持?<br />\n勝利係咪最後會屬於香港人？<br />\n最後<br />\n多謝前線手足<br />\n我好廢<br />\n我連想像自己係前線我都覺得驚<br />\n但你地為左香港一直衝係最前<br />\n甚至受傷都未必可以報警或求醫<br />\n多謝你地<br />\n我會繼續係後方用我可以做既野去支持你地<br />\n結果點都好<br />\n真心多謝你地！！！"},{"pid":"5660b45421f88676f1540ca0ed8ad2bf32cdbe7e","tid":1503401,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74daa020a62df8ee1b7ad994b407ac4a352cba9b","tid":1503401,"uid":300229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c1d564586f598bec65ceaf7bfd1e423804c7b42f","tid":1503401,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEhtr7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEhtr7b.png&h=d0ab0272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style